item.name: 通过指纹ID获取门锁用户名

request.description:
This API endpoint allows you to retrieve the smart lock user name associated with a specific fingerprint ID. The HTTP POST request should be made to {{am_url}}/v3/am/get_smart_lock_userName_fingerprintId.

### Request Body

The request should include the following payload in the raw request body type:

``` json
{
    "header": {
        "device_list": ["3LXPGSZXD373MKP2111A"],
        "seqno": "202410311607568710959401357102",
        "user_id": "57e31ee1248e322ba4e5ed0b37f18a ...",
        "package_name": "com.jooan.qiaoanzhilian",
        "language": "zh_CN",
        "client_version": "5.3.18.81",
        "token": "76b245c62ee346628c29",
        "phone_model": "22120RN86C"
    },
    "smartLockFingerprintPwdId": 1,
    "smartLockFingerprintType": 1
}

 ```

### Response

Upon successful execution, the API returns a status code of 200 and a response with the content type of text/plain. The response body contains the following fields:

``` json
{
    "error_code": "",
    "error_msg": "",
    "smartLockUserName": ""
}

 ```

### Example Response

``` json
{
    "error_code": "",
    "error_msg": "",
    "smartLockUserName": ""
}

 ```
